s.\nThe agreement with findings in other nearby radio galaxies suggests that this\nis not an isolated case, and probably the paradigm of AGN feedback through\nradio jets, at least for galaxies hosting low-luminosity active nuclei.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2016 20:00:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-05"}
