rivial topography, and a last experiment of slow Rossby modes simulating\nthe displacement of a baroclinic vortex subject to the Coriolis force.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Jul 2016 10:54:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Jan 2017 14:52:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-24"}
