$XY$ models in the presence of a magnetic field. In particular, we\nconfirm that the topological hypothesis holds for both the infinite-range ($T_c\n\\neq 0$) and the short-range ($T_c = 0$) $XY$ models. Further studies are very\ndesirable in order to clarify the extension of the validity of our proposal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Jul 2016 10:29:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-01"}
